 ve a finished film. The public grant page does not state geographic restri
 ctions\, age limits or career-stage requirements - confirm on the linked p
 age before applying. Apply via the Google Form linked from the festival's 
 grant-info page.\n\nOrganisation: Grove and Pines Film Festival (GAPFF)\nL
 ocation: United States (festival is US-based\; geographic eligibility not 
 specified on the grant page)\nAward: $5\,000 USD grant awarded annually at
