 . Strong fit for narrative writers using fiction to dramatise climate\, ec
 ology\, energy\, or environmental-justice themes (rather than documentary)
 .\n\nOrganisation: Natural Resources Defense Council (NRDC) in partnership
  with The Black List\nLocation: United States (verify international eligib
